mat: bath_height (lat, long)
var: latitude
var: longitude 
var: date
var: hb_depth

Computation function outputs:
mat/arr: dTdz_peaks (z, T)
mat/arr: const_consec (z,T)

Functions callable (computation):
 - grad_spike(data, gradient, threshold)
 - T_spike(data, threshold)
